wikibaseimport-importentity-explanation:
Explanation of what this special page does. This text is displayed on the special page above the entity ID form. Parameters:
* $1 contains a link to the remote (source) Wikibase installation from which entities are imported.
wikibaseimport-importentity-form-section: Header of the section of the entity ID form.
wikibaseimport-importentity-form-submit-: Label for the button that starts the import.
wikibaseimport-importentity-form-entityi: Label for the entity ID input field.
Entity ID placeholder for the input field.
wikibaseimport-importentity-form-imports: Label for the “import statements” checkbox. This feature is not supported yet, so the checkbox is disabled.
wikibaseimport-importentity-error-no-loc: Page title of the error page for when the local entity ID to redirect to cannot be found.
Error message for when the local entity ID to redirect to cannot be found.
